    <sec id="sec5h">
      <title>Cell culture</title>
      <p>SK-N-SH, IMR32, T47D, HCC1143 and HMEC cells were purchased from the American Type Culture Collection and maintained at 37<inline-formula><tex-math notation="LaTeX" id="ImEquation12">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
