      </table-wrap>
      <p>The upper maximum number of fragments that could be generated in the lookup table can be calculated with equation <xref rid="deqn05" ref-type="disp-formula">5</xref> when <italic toggle="yes">m</italic> is maximum length, <italic toggle="yes">k</italic> is minimum length, <italic toggle="yes">i</italic> is the ith source transcript, <italic toggle="yes">j</italic> is the number of source transcripts and <italic toggle="yes">n</italic> is the length of the transcript: </p>
      <disp-formula id="deqn01">
